    "title": "バブリーランドいらっしゃいませ",
    "enTitle": "Welcome to Bubblyland",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『バブリーランド』――そこは、バブル時代の浮かれた雰囲気を\r\n愛するオーナーによって作られた、奇妙キテレツなプールリゾート。",
            "enText": "Bubblyland is an eccentric pool resort built by \nan owner infatuated with the fun atmosphere \nof Japan's late '80s bubble era.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -5503495990840030219,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ここでは皆『あの頃』のパッションと輝きを求めて己を開放し、\r\n非日常に満ちた世界を闊歩するのだ――",
            "enText": "Here, everyone liberates themselves in their desire \nto experience the passion and brilliance of the good \nol' days and a taste of the extraordinary.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 43628312314397709,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "マルゼンスキー",
            "enName": "Maruzensky",
            "jpText": "ディスコにはお立ち台、サ店でティラミスにナタデココ、\r\nプールにはモチ、巨大なウォータースライダーよーっ！",
            "enText": "There's podiums to dance on, tiramisu and nata de coco at \nthe cafe, mochi by the pool, and a giant waterslide to enjoy!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 222,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": -642797035760251981
                },
