            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "わあ～！　見てください！\r\n外の駐車場に、低く改造された車がたくさん――",
            "enText": "Wow! Look at those cars! \nTheir bodies are set so low to the ground!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
